title: 1 killed, 4 others injured in shooting at a hookah lounge near Virginia Tech's main campus, police say - CNN
content: 1 killed, 4 others injured in shooting at a hookah lounge near Virginia Tech's main campus, police say  CNN
description: One person was killed and four others were injured in a shooting late Friday at a hookah lounge near Virginia Tech's campus in downtown Blacksburg, police said.
